<wxs module="filters" src="../fliter.wxs"></wxs>
<view class="header">
  <view class="orderList">
     <navigator class="orderModal" hover-class="none" url="orderinfo">
      <view class="orderDetail">
        <view class="image">
          <!-- <image src="../../images/product/oppo.png"/> -->
          <image src="{{order.goods_image}}"/> 
        </view>
        <view class="proInfo">
          <view class="title">{{order.goods_name}}</view>
          <view>规格：{{sku_name}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </navigator>
  </view>
  <view class="orderInfo">
    <view class='title'>费用明细</view>
    <view class="flex rent">
      <view>总租金</view>
      <view>￥{{order.real_total_amount}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="flex">
      <view>意外保障服务费</view>
      <view>￥{{order.insu_cost}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="flex">
      <view>期数</view>
      <view>{{order.period}}期（25天/期）</view>
    </view>

    <view class="flex money">
      <view>分期费用</view>
      <view>￥{{filters.toFix(order.real_total_amount/order.period)}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="alert">
      <view><image src="../../images/product/alert.png"/></view>
      <view>您每期需要还款的费用。差额部分将在最后一期补齐。</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="orderInfo">
    <view class='title'>预授权明细</view>
    <view class="flex">
      <view>预授权总金额</view>
      <view>￥{{order.real_freeze}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="flex">
      <view>到期还机解冻金额</view>
      <view>￥{{order.deposit}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="flex way">
      <view>预授权冻结方式</view>
      <view>信用卡</view>
    </view>
    <view class="alert">
      <view><image src="../../images/product/alert.png"/></view>
      <view>预授权冻结无利息，不会产生附加费用。</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="orderInfo">
    <view class='title'>租期信息</view>
    <view class="flex">
      <view>下单日期</view>
      <view>{{order.add_time}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="flex">
      <view>租赁到期日期</view>
      <view>{{order.order_time}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="flex">
      <view>意外保障生效日期</view>
      <view>{{order.insu_time}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="flex choose">
      <view>到期可选</view>
      <view>买断或还机</view>
    </view>
    <view class="alert">
      <view><image src="../../images/product/alert.png"/></view>
      <view>最后还机日期为租赁到期日期后的第7天，是指易享优租收到机器的时间，而非用户寄出机器的时间。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="agree">
    <view class="readArg">
      <view><image src="../../images/product/choose.png"/></view>
      <view>我已阅读并同意
        <text>《易享优租用户协议》、</text>
        <text>《易享优租意外保障服务协议》、</text>
        <text>《个人消费分期合同》</text>
      </view>
    </view>      
  </view>
</view>

<view class="footer">
  <view class="btn full" bindtap="getConfirm">确定提交</view>
</view>